node.text:
🍹😎 When you take the summer off after finishing residency and fellowship. 🙌🏼🎊 Have loved traveling and spending time with friends and family. 🌍🥰 Looking forward to the next chapter! ☀️🌴 P.S. My mom told me I should post this pic. 🙃
•
#ibiza #spain #europe #vacation #doctor #physician #wellness #mentalhealth #summer #workhard #playhard #tb

@choosechicago @tiesto @gryffinofficial @bettywho @chakaikhan @prideintheparkchicago @pridefestchicago @dustygeauxtigers

node.text:
As a physician to my patients and as a friend and family member to my loved ones, I think that good mental health is so important to a happy and healthy life. I’ve partnered with The LifeStance Health Foundation who is donating $5 (up to $250k) to the Mental Health Coalition (@mentalhealthcoalition ) for every message sharing mental health stories with the hashtag #Not1Face. 

With so many of my patients in chronic pain, I see mental health comorbidities very frequently. It is so important to bring about better awareness and resources for people suffering from these illnesses. Anxiety and depression have haunted so many of my friends and family throughout the years and are becoming strikingly more prevalent in younger generations. I myself have even experienced aspects of anxiety and depression throughout my long road of medical training and while struggling with religion and sexuality. It is so important that we acknowledge these issues and come together to help each other overcome in order to be a healthier and happier society. 

Head to the @lifestancehealth link in my bio for more information. Feel free to share your stories as well!
